### ProfileHub API - Exemplos de Requisições

### Variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = 

### ===== AUTENTICAÇÃO =====

### Registrar novo usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "novo@example.com",
  "username": "novo_usuario",
  "password": "SenhaForte123!",
  "firstName": "João",
  "lastName": "Silva"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "novo@example.com",
  "password": "SenhaForte123!"
}

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ===== USUÁRIOS =====

### Obter usuário atual
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obter usuário por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar perfil de usuário
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "João",
  "lastName": "Silva",
  "bio": "Desenvolvedor fullstack",
  "profilePictureUrl": "https://example.com/image.jpg"
}

### Alterar senha
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/1/change-password?oldPassword=SenhaForte123!&newPassword=NovaSenha456!
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Deletar usuário
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===== DOCUMENTOS =====

### Upload de documento (usando arquivo de teste)
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="documento.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./documents/sample.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Documento importante para análise
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="isPublic"

false
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Obter documento
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar documentos do usuário
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/user/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar documentos do usuário (paginado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/user/documents/paginated?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar documentos públicos
GET {{baseUrl}}/documents/public?page=0&size=10

### Atualizar documento
PUT {{baseUrl}}/documents/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Descrição atualizada",
  "isPublic": true
}

### Deletar documento
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/documents/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===== CASOS DE ERRO =====

### Login com email inválido
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "inexistente@example.com",
  "password": "senhaqualquer"
}

### Registro com email já existente
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "novo@example.com",
  "username": "outro_usuario",
  "password": "SenhaForte123!",
  "firstName": "Maria",
  "lastName": "Santos"
}

### Acesso sem token
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me

### Token inválido
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer token_invalido

### Documento que não pertence ao usuário
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/documents/999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
